verbose_text: Inhibition of the expression of Hsp27 with siRNA or OGX-427, an antisense oligonucleotide in phase II trials, synergistically enhanced the efficacy of EGFR tyrosine kinase inhibitor XREF_BIBR, radiation XREF_BIBR, Hsp90 inhibitor XREF_BIBR, MET inhibitor XREF_BIBR, paclitaxel XREF_BIBR.
